channel.title: New error when I run the server!
channel.description: I have no idea why this happened. I think it happened after I used some item editor to edit item.cfg, but I might be wrong. Now, this keeps me from even going into my server with any account. I just get a black screen. [IMG]http://i156.photobucket.com/albums/t32/Flamingice07/servererror.jpg[/img]

item.title: New error when I run the server!
item.dc:creator: @Land Land
item.description:
@Land wrote:

Sorry for being the biggest nub on earth, but what do I do in item.cfg? I get the error when I RUN the server. The compiling is fine, just not when I run the server. I already tried that and it didn’t work anyway.

EDIT: I fixed it now, the retarded item.cfg editor I was using didn’t put tabs and underscores in, so I had to replace it with the original TestScape one. Oh well… At least it’s fixed.
